	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="0" /><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Niet nu, <delay20 />oké? <anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ik ben te boos om
