	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Als je het begrijpt<tag a="110" b="0" /> <anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />dan hoeven we
